Package com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob

Class BlobConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.blob.BlobConfiguration

  • public abstract class BlobConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains static strings used to identify parts of a service configuration instance associated with the Windows Azure Blob service.

    These values must not be altered.

      • ACCOUNT_NAME

        public static final java.lang.String ACCOUNT_NAME
        The Blob configuration account name constant. This String value is used as a key in the configuration file, to identify the value for the DNS prefix name for the storage account.

        public static final java.lang.String URI
        The Blob configuration URI constant. This String value is used as a key in the configuration file, to identify the URI value for the Blob storage service REST API address for the storage account.
